<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/gsap.min.js"></script>

    <style>
      /* Global Light Mode Styles */

/* Global Light Mode Styles */
body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f9fafb;
    color: #1f2937;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.help-content {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
}

.help-section h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #2563eb;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.faq-item {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

.faq-question {
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    color: #2563eb;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    background-color: #f0f9ff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
}

.faq-question:hover {
    background-color: #dbeafe;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.faq-answer {
    max-height: 0; /* Collapsed by default */
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, opacity 0.4s ease;
    opacity: 0; /* Collapsed by default */
    padding: 0 0.75rem;
    color: #4b5563;
}

.faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    max-height: 200px; /* Enough height to show the content */
    opacity: 1; /* Make it visible */
    padding: 0.75rem; /* Padding when visible */
    background-color: #ffffff; /* Background for visible answer */
    border-left: 3px solid #2563eb; /* Border style */
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; /* Rounded bottom corners */
}

/* Call-to-Action Button */
.cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background-color: #2563eb;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #1d4ed8;
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Dark Mode Styles */
.dark-mode {
    background-color: #1c1c1c;
    color: #f9fafb;
}

.dark-mode .help-content {
    background-color: #374151;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.dark-mode .faq-question {
    color: #60a5fa;
    background-color: #1f2937;
    border-bottom-color: #4b5563;
}

.dark-mode .faq-question:hover {
    background-color: #283241;
}

.dark-mode .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    background-color: #1f2937;
    border-left-color: #60a5fa;
    color: #d1d5db;

}

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="progress-bar"></div>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="help-content">
      <section class="help-section">
        <h1>FAQs</h1>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">What is Scruter?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Scruter is your local platform for buying, selling, and discovering everything you need. Whether it's products, services, or community activities, we connect people for a better local experience.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How can I buy or sell items on Scruter?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            You can create an account, list your items for sale, or browse items available in your local area through our user-friendly interface.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Is there a fee for using Scruter?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Scruter is free to use for buying and selling. However, we may charge a small fee for premium listings or features in the future.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How can I contact customer support?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            If you have any questions or need assistance, you can reach our customer support team at scruter@gmail.com or call us at 999999999.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">What should I do if I encounter a problem with a transaction?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            If you experience any issues with a transaction, please contact our support team immediately, and we will assist you in resolving the matter.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Can I edit or delete my listings?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Yes, you can edit or delete your listings anytime through your account dashboard.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How can I reset my password?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            If you've forgotten your password, you can reset it by clicking on the "Forgot Password?" link on the login page and following the instructions.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">What payment methods are accepted on Scruter?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards and popular online payment systems. Specific payment options will be listed at checkout.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Can I leave reviews for buyers or sellers?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Yes! After completing a transaction, you can leave reviews for buyers or sellers based on your experience to help others make informed decisions.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Is my personal information safe on Scruter?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Yes, we take your privacy seriously. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. Please review our privacy policy for more details.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">How do I report a user or listing?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            If you encounter suspicious activity or listings, please contact our support team with the details, and we will investigate the matter promptly.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">Can I access Scruter from my mobile device?</div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Yes, Scruter is optimized for mobile use, so you can browse, buy, and sell items directly from your smartphone or tablet.
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Contact Support</a>
      </section>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %> 
    <%- include('partials/bottom_nav') %>

    <script>
document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const parentItem = item.closest('.faq-item');
        parentItem.classList.toggle('active'); // Toggle active class

        // Optionally close other questions
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(otherItem => {
            if (otherItem !== parentItem) {
                otherItem.classList.remove('active');
            }
        });
    });
});
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
